'''iPhone 15''' and '''iPhone 15 Plus''' are to be released products in the [[iPhone]] line of [[Smartphone|smartphones]] made by [[Apple Inc.|Apple]] which may be released sometime in between September 15, 2023 and October 7, 2023.<ref name=":0">{{Cite web |title=iPhone 15: Everything We Know |url=https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/iphone-15/ |access-date=2022-09-02 |website=MacRumors |language=en}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web |last=Livemint |date=2022-10-11 |title=iPhone 15: How a note to Apple Store employees may have leaked its launch date |url=https://www.livemint.com/technology/gadgets/iphone-15-how-a-note-to-apple-store-employees-may-have-leaked-its-launch-date-11665465018083.html |access-date=2022-10-11 |website=mint |language=en}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web |last=gargi.chaudhry |title=iPhone 15 launched date leaked? Here's what we know so far |url=https://newsable.asianetnews.com/gadget-technology/apple-iphone-15-launched-date-leaked-here-is-what-we-know-so-far-gcw-rjkvve |access-date=2022-10-11 |website=Asianet News Network Pvt Ltd |language=en}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite web |title=Apple iPhone 15 launch date reportedly leaked by Apple Store employee |url=https://www.dnaindia.com/technology/report-apple-iphone-15-launch-date-reportedly-leaked-by-apple-store-employee-2991931 |access-date=2022-10-11 |website=DNA India |language=en}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite web |date=2022-10-10 |title=iPhone 15 release date LEAKED? Just check this out |url=https://tech.hindustantimes.com/mobile/news/iphone-15-release-date-leaked-just-check-this-out-71665414549452.html |access-date=2022-10-11 |website=HT Tech |language=en}}</ref> These phones are to be released with [[Draft:IOS 17|iOS 17]], which is in the [[iOS]] line of software made by [[Apple Inc.|Apple]].

