iPhone 15: $799

iPhone 15 Plus: $899

=== Dynamic Island ===
The Dynamic Island may come to the non-Pro iPhone 15s.

=== Release Date ===
The iPhone 15 lineup may be launching sometime in between September 15, 2023 and October 7, 2023.<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" /><ref name=":3" /><ref name=":4" />

